## Usage and Implementation

While specific API endpoints aren't detailed in the documentation, Compass appears to be accessed through the Amplitude web interface. Users can:

1. Select a base cohort (typically new users)
2. Define a target cohort (retained users)
3. Specify the range of first use and performance days
4. View the resulting heat map of correlations
5. Create cohorts based on findings
6. Export or share insights with team members

Compass helps product teams answer critical questions like "What behaviors predict user retention?" and "How many times must users perform an action to become retained?" - enabling data-driven product development and growth strategies.